sources.title: Go for It 1983 | Terence Hill, Bud Spencer | Two Misfits, One Mission | Full Movie
sources.description:
Two men meet in a strange situation and end up being mistaken first for robbers, then for Secret Service agents.

Original title: Nati con la camicia
Alternative title: Trinity: Hits the Road

Director: Enzo Barboni
Writer: Marco Barboni
Stars: Terence Hill, Bud Spencer, Buffy Dee
Genres: Action, Adventure, Comedy

00:00 – Full movie
02:26 – Mason and Rosco meet under unusual circumstances, leading to a case of mistaken identity.
08:53 – Mason defies the rules by unloading his truck, resulting in a violent altercation and a police chase.
17:56 – Rosco and Mason are mistaken for criminals and forced onto a plane, receiving a mysterious briefcase.
27:54 – The duo, now undercover agents, embark on a mission in Miami, facing unexpected challenges.
37:30 – Equipped with disguises and gadgets, they are tasked with thwarting a mind-boggling plan.
54:07 – The pair find themselves entangled with Chinese criminals over a hamburger dispute.
1:08:08 – Mason is pursued by hitmen and interrogated about Steinberg's whereabouts.
1:29:52 – A villain plans to launch a missile to intercept a space shuttle, aiming to spread a deadly cloud of radiation.


Countries of origin: Italy, United States
